Paper: hep-th/0008039

Date: 2000-08-03

Title: Differential equations for general SU(n) Bethe ansatz systems

Authors: Patrick Dorey, Clare Dunning and Roberto Tateo

Comments: 19 pages and no figures. LaTex2e, uses amssymb and cite.V2

added, minor typos correctedJournal-ref: J.Phys. A33 (2000) 8427-8442

We show that SU(n) Bethe Ansatz equations with arbitrary `twist' parametersare hidden inside certain nth order ordinary differential equations, anddiscuss various consequences of this fact.